author: Bradford Betz
title: Protests planned in Vermont over governor’s coronavirus restrictions; police say it may tie up traffic
description: A gun-rights group is organizing a demonstration around the Vermont State Capitol on Wednesday to protest the governor’s stay-out-home order amid the COVID-19 pandemic.
